Summary: Colour Management System
Name: oyranos
License: GPL
Group: Development/Libraries
URL: http://www.oyranos.org
Vendor: Kai-Uwe Behrmann
Packager: Kai-Uwe Behrmann <ku.b@gmx.de>
BuildArch: noarch
BuildRoot: %{_tmppath}/%{name}-root
Prefix:    %{_prefix}

%description
Oyranos is a colour management configuration system.
It is primarily developed on free operating systems.
Developers from other OSes can jump in the current
discussion to make Oyranos aware of cross platform
standards. Feel cordially invited to make constructive
suggestions.

Authors:
--------
    Oyranos     Kai-Uwe Behrmann <www.behrmann.name>

used components and libraries with divergine FOSS licenses:
    Elektra     Avi Alkalay and others
    md5         L. Peter Deutsch
    libXNVCtrl  Nvidia


%prep
%setup -q -n %{name}-%{version}

%build
%configure --quick --enable-verbose

%install
rm -rf %{buildroot}
make DESTDIR=%{buildroot} install-icc
rm -fr %{buildroot}/%{_datadir}/doc/%{name}

%clean
rm -rf %{buildroot}

%post
%postun


%package      RGB
Summary:    Oyranos standard sRGB ICC profile +
Group:      Applications/Graphics
Vendor:     http://www.littlecms.com
URL:        http://www.littlecms.com
License:    public domain
Version:    0.4
%description  RGB
The "WWW standard" sRGB profile and others

%package      lcmsLAB
Summary:    Oyranos standard PCS profiles
Group:      Applications/Graphics
Vendor:     http://www.littlecms.com
URL:        http://www.littlecms.com
License:    public domain
Version:    0.5
%description  lcmsLAB
Special LCMS profiles.

%package      LStarRGB
Summary:    Oyranos standard Editing RGB profile
Group:      Applications/Graphics
Vendor:     http://www.lstar-rgb.com
URL:        http://www.lstar-rgb.com
License:    LStar-RGB
Version:    0.4
%description  LStarRGB
The RGB profile maintaining perceptual equal lightness.

%package      Cineon
Summary:    Oyranos additional Cineon ICC Profiles
Group:      Applications/Graphics
URL:        http://www.behrmann.name
License:    GPL
Version:    0.4
%description  Cineon
Cineon ICC Profiles

%package      PhotoGamutRGB
Summary:    Oyranos additional ICC Profile for Photoediting
Group:      Applications/Graphics
Vendor:     http://www.photogamut.org
URL:        http://www.photogamut.org
License:    PhotoGamut
Version:    0.4
%description  PhotoGamutRGB
A ICC Profile optimized for digital photos.

%package      eci-offset2004
Summary:    ECI Offset-Profiles 2004
Group:      Applications/Graphics
URL:        http://www.eci.org
Vendor:     http://www.eci.org
License:    Commercial Heidelberg
Version:    1.1
%description  eci-offset2004
ECI Offset-Profiles according to ISO 12647-2. These are CMYK
ICC profiles for ISO printing conditions. See http://eci.org for
detailed specifications.


